snippet.title: DarkViperAU
snippet.description:
My channel primarily focuses on Grand Theft Auto V speed and challenge runs. I also playthrough other GTA games and clones with a decent amount of comedy and commentary thrown in. Series include ‘How the speedrun ended’, ‘A speedrunner rambles’, ‘Can you complete GTA V without wasting anyone?’, ‘Completing GTA V without taking damage’, and ‘GTA V facts and glitches you don’t know’.
